archimate:Principle.name: Sovrin Glossary
archimate:Principle.documentation: An alphabetically sorted list of terms used in the Sovrin Governance Framework, each of which has a short description (definition) and optionally additional text that provides further explanation. The Sovrin Glossary (i.e. the present document) is a Controlled Document of the Sovrin Governance Framework.
